    "title": "Career Opportunity Software Engineer at IBM India International Enterprises",
    "description": "IBM India International Enterprises has an exciting opening for a Software Engineer at our Nashik office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout IBM India International Enterprises:\nIBM India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Master's degree preferred\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in JavaScript\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in MongoDB\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Git\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with IBM India International Enterprises!",
